name: Felt Food Veggetables
description:
All items are made to order.

All items are hand made with Eco-Friendly Felt and 100% Polyester fiberfill.

Set Includes:

- One Tomato
- One Carrot
- One Eggplant

All items are made by hand and may vary in size slightly as each piece is one of a kind. 
Not recommended for children under two years old.
